{
  "stem": "2226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I got that here in the book too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they come, like, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a little like here, you got [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a conference at that time-- Hitler with Goebbels, Goering, you know, Hess-- they all-- they all went-- Hossler and Koch.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they all-- they got-- they all got together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they called and went for a conference in a villa not far from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They called it Wannsee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING] He thought it was the solution to try-- to kill all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was Eichmann at that time, Rosenberg, Waldheim, I guess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Waldheim, I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "100.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "100 in the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "100 in the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You sat like that first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Any-- the young fellows like me I had a position already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I drove a big truck, because like we had trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I learned myself to back up the truck like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when I come to Auschwitz, turn towards home back, so a gendarme came out in the marketplace because [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know what that means?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every Jew that was in the city has to come out on the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If not, you'll be killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They'll shoot you right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If they went to  a house, and they find somebody, they shoot you right away right on the spot-- not a-- not such a thing, but, yes, shoot you right away.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I told mother I'm going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She started to cry, don't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Don't go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I said, I have to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If they catch me, it's no good anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I come to the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
